targets.query: SELECT 100 - mean("usage_idle") FROM "cpu" WHERE host =~ /$host/ AND pod =~ /$pod/ AND "region" =~ /^$region/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "host" fill(null)
SELECT mean("used_percent") FROM "disk" WHERE host =~ /$host/ AND pod =~ /$pod/ AND "region" =~ /^$region/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "host", "path" fill(null)
SELECT mean("value") FROM "openldap_value" WHERE "type_instance" = 'threads-active' AND service =~ /ldap*/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(null)
SELECT mean("value") FROM "openldap_value" WHERE "type_instance" = 'threads-backload' AND service =~ /ldap*/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(null)
SELECT mean("value") FROM "openldap_value" WHERE "type_instance" = 'threads-open' AND service =~ /ldap*/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(null)
SELECT mean("value") FROM "openldap_value" WHERE "type_instance" = 'threads-pending' AND service =~ /ldap*/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(null)
SELECT mean("starting") FROM "ldapthreads" WHERE "type_instance" = 'threads-starting' AND service =~ /ldap*/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(null)
SELECT mean("value") FROM "openldap_value" WHERE "type_instance" = 'waiters-read' AND service =~ /ldap*/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(null)
SELECT mean("value") FROM "cpu" WHERE "service" = 'postgres' AND "metric_db" = 'select tag value' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(null)
SELECT mean("value") FROM "openldap_value" WHERE "type_instance" = 'statistics-pdu' AND service =~ /ldap*/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(null)
SELECT mean("value") FROM "openldap_value" WHERE "type_instance" = 'statistics-entries' AND service =~ /ldap*/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(null)
SELECT mean("value") FROM "openldap_value" WHERE "type_instance" = 'statistics-referrals' AND service =~ /ldap*/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(null)
SELECT mean("value") FROM "ldap_value" WHERE "type_instance" = 'heartbeat-searchTime' AND service =~ /ldap*/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(null)
SELECT derivative(mean("packets_recv"), 1s) FROM "net" WHERE host =~ /$host/ AND pod =~ /$pod/ AND "region" =~ /^$region/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "host" fill(null)
SELECT derivative(mean("packets_sent"), 1s) FROM "net" WHERE host =~ /$host/ AND pod =~ /$pod/ AND "region" =~ /^$region/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "host" fill(null)
SELECT mean("Current") FROM "ldapConnections" WHERE "service" = 'ldap' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "host" fill(null)
